data.description: This home is priced to sell! Nice ranch conveniently located to shopping, and restaurants.  Flat corner lot in the heart of Pearisburg. Beautiful hard wood floors and lots and lots of storage. Listed as a three bedroom but could easily be used as a four or five bedroom.  Spacious covered back patio. This home is being sold as is where is. With a little TLC this home could be a jewel.
